  "Description": {
    "English": "A high-performance <span class=\"name name-stellar\">solar sail</span>, deployed automatically during flight. This advanced <span class=\"name name-technology\">propulsion device</span> generates an electric field within the sails themselves, allowing the starship to build momentum from the solar wind.<br><br>Offers substantial gains in <span class=\"name name-stellar\">fuel efficiency</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">boost</span> performance over conventional engine systems, as well as enabling photovoltaic <span class=\"name name-stellar\">recharge</span> of the starship's <span class=\"name name-technology\">launch systems</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一面高性能<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太阳能帆</span>，能在飞行过程中自动部署。这种先进的<span class=\"name name-technology\">推进装置</span>在帆内产生电场，使飞船能够从太阳风中获得动力。<br><br>该技术相较传统的驱动器系统在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">燃料效率</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">增压</span>性能方面有极大提高，同时还能为飞船的<span class=\"name name-technology\">发射系统</span>进行光伏<span class=\"name name-stellar\">充电</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "高性能的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太陽能帆</span>，會在飛行過程中自動展開。這種先進的<span class=\"name name-technology\">推進裝置</span>會在帆內產生電場，讓太空船從太陽風中累積動力。<br><br>能夠大幅提高<span class=\"name name-stellar\">燃料效率</span>，並且比傳統引擎系統更能夠<span class=\"name name-stellar\">增強</span>性能，可使用光電<span class=\"name name-stellar\">充能</span>太空船的<span class=\"name name-technology\">啟動系統</span>。"
  },
